com.kontakt.sdk.android.ble.discovery.eddystone

Interface EddystoneTLMAdvertisingPacket


  • public interface EddystoneTLMAdvertisingPacket
    Eddystone TLM advertising packet. The telemetry packet provides information The TLM advertising packet has the following structure:
    • [0] - TLM version
    • [1]..[2] - battery voltage
    • [3]..[4] - beacon temperature
    • [5]..[8] - Advertising PDU Count
    • [9]..[12] - Second resolution counter
